    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "rebuild? what is there to even rebuild. the people i knew, the respect i had... they don't even recognize me anymore. even my family looks at me like i'm some kind of cautionary tale. it's not just a setback, it feels like the version of me that actually existed is just... extinct. i don't see how any of that comes back.",
